<slide fontsize="6em">
	<title>Script Encoding</title>
	<subtitle>Setting Script Encoding With declare()</subtitle>

	<blurb>Interpreting an iso-8859-1 script as UTF-8:</blurb>
	<example><![CDATA[<?php
	declare(encoding="iso-8859-1");
	$str = "blå = 青";
	var_inspect($str);
?>]]></example>
